Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:05.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,およそ遠しとされしもの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:08.44,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,下等で奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:13.95,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,見慣れた動植物とはまるで違うと思しきもの達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:17.58,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それら異形の一群を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:20.58,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,人は古くから畏れを含み
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:23.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いつしか総じて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.67,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,「蟲」と呼んだ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:03.23,0:00:05.98,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0,0,0,,一群遥远的存在
Dialogue: 1,0:00:06.90,0:00:08.44,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0,0,0,,下等且奇怪
Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.07,0:00:13.95,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0,0,0,,与已知动植物截然不同的存在
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.07,0:00:17.58,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0,0,0,,这些奇异的一类
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.83,0:00:20.58,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0,0,0,,自古以来为人类所畏惧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.37,0:00:23.21,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0,0,0,,不知何时开始
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.67,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0,0,0,,称之为「虫」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:48.90,OP EN Footlight MT Light,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fad(600,800)}We broke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:51.23,OP EN Footlight MT Light,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fad(600,800)}Everything that was right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:54.11,OP EN Footlight MT Light,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fad(600,800)}We both enjoyed a good fight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:56.66,OP EN Footlight MT Light,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fad(600,800)}And we sweded
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:59.08,OP EN Footlight MT Light,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fad(600,800)}All the holes we had to breathe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.87,OP EN Footlight MT Light,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fad(600,800)}To make the other one leave
