Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:22.22,OP EN Footlight MT Light,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fad(600,1000)}When we were alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:30.48,OP EN Footlight MT Light,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fad(600,800)}And I'll shiver like I used to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:37.82,OP EN Footlight MT Light,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fad(600,800)}And I'll leave him just for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:46.04,OP EN Footlight MT Light,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fad(600,1200)}And I'll shiver like I used to
